biblScope></bibl></cit>, cf. <bibl n=\"urn:cts:greekLit:tlg4083.tlg001:1951:2\" default=\"NO\" TEIform=\"bibl\"> <author TEIform=\"author\"><a class=\"S\" href=\"S:LSJ Eust.\">Eust.</a></author> <biblScope TEIform=\"biblScope\">1951.2</biblScope></bibl>, <bibl default=\"NO\" TEIform=\"bibl\"> <author TEIform=\"author\"><a class=\"S\" href=\"S:LSJ Hsch.\">Hsch.</a></author> </bibl>: the deriv. from <foreign lang=\"greek\" TEIform=\"foreign\">ὀξύς</foreign> is less probable.</sense> </entryFree>"}]}